genresAdvancedInfo.name: marathi devotional
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Marathi devotional music is a genre of music that is deeply rooted in the spiritual traditions of Maharashtra. These songs are often sung in praise of Hindu deities and saints, and are performed in temples and other religious settings. They feature richly layered melodies and powerful vocals, and are a central part of Marathi culture.
